Give the equivalent of a decimal number in other bases
Please only write the digits 0-F for hex, 0-7 for octal, 0-1 for binary 0-3 for base 4
The number 777 in hexadecimal is 
0309

The number 777 in octal is 
01411

The number 777 in binary is 
1100001001

The number 777 to the base 4 is 
30021
 
